(National Assembly), [Hearing Day 55 – Prof Thuli Madonsela to appear before the Committee], Hybrid (Committee Room M46 & Virtual Meeting Platform), 09:00-17:00Show less • Editor's note: This live event has ended. You may watch a recording above. CAPE TOWN - Former Public Protector Thuli Madonsela finally took the stand at the Section 194 inquiry into suspended Public Protector Busisiwe Mkhwebane. She returns to the hot seat today. And her appearance was characterised by heated exchanges with Mkhwebane's legal representative, Dali Mpofu.